@startuml
hide footbox
actor Client
participant "order-service" as Order
queue "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "fulfillment-service" as Fulfillment
participant "carrier webhook" as Carrier
participant "notification-service" as Notification

Order -> Kafka: OrderPlaced
Kafka -> Fulfillment: consume OrderPlaced
Fulfillment -> Fulfillment: create shipment and assign warehouse
Fulfillment -> Kafka: ShipmentCreated
Carrier -> Fulfillment: tracking status update
Fulfillment -> Kafka: ShipmentStatusChanged
Kafka -> Notification: consume shipment event
Client -> Notification: subscribe via WebSocket
Notification --> Client: tracking update pushed in real time
@enduml
